entries.s_11: I know. So you have to talk fast. Where are the crash survivors?
entries.s_13: They left for Nashal, %TO. They planned to make camp at coordinates 6037, 7023. The rest of them went in search of the missing crew. I don't know where they are, but I remember the captain making everyone wear tracking emitters. He gave me the password for the tracking device for safe keeping, but I seem to have misplaced the device.
entries.s_16: Listen to me. I need to know the password for the tracking device.
entries.s_20: Yes, hurry. I need it so I can save your owners from the creatures.
entries.s_22: Yes, of course, %TO! The password is AX5TT17.
